WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.000
We figured all about the abduction and abuse of Ms. Erika six years ago, so here's a detailed report.

2
00:00:07.740 --> 00:00:09.800
Someone's trying to hurt Mommy.

3
00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:28.160
We found evidence six years ago.

4
00:00:28.160 --> 00:00:30.510
Dad and I took Erika away.

5
00:00:30.510 --> 00:00:44.939
I beat your tool again. I am following my own will.

6
00:00:44.939 --> 00:00:47.770
Never this.

7
00:00:47.770 --> 00:00:55.060
I'll respect you because you're the father of the woman I love, but if you lay a hand on her again, you'll pay a thousand times over.

8
00:00:55.060 --> 00:00:58.060
So this is the wild man you found outside?

9
00:00:58.060 --> 00:01:04.250
He's nothing special. No manners. The Morrison's will make you a great new existence.

10
00:01:04.250 --> 00:01:09.409
Let them come. We'll see you regrets at first. Ben, get them out of here.

11
00:01:09.409 --> 00:01:21.000
My dad and Dan's dad here in Morrison. I don't know what they might do.

12
00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.579
I'm scared they might hurt you.

13
00:01:23.579 --> 00:01:27.409
Don't worry. They can't hurt us.

14
00:01:27.409 --> 00:01:32.409
Compared to my family or nothing. Do you know anything with them? It's a piece of cake.

